-- MOVES-Northern Trust Asset appoints global head for ESG investing
-- 
-- Wed Jun 25, 2014 08:05AM EDT
-- None



June 25 (Reuters) - Northern Trust Asset Management, a part of Northern Trust Corp <NTRS.O>, appointed Mamadou-Abou Sarr as global head of environmental, social and governance (ESG) investing.   (Reporting by Avik Das in Bangalore)  ((Bangalore newsroom)(moves@thomsonreuters.com))  Keywords: FINANCIAL MOVES/NORTHERNTRUSTASSETMANAGEMENT

